text: Henri Matter (1901 - 30 May 1983) was a French swimmer. He competed in the men's 100 metre backstroke event at the 1920 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1901 births Category:1983 deaths Category:French male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of France Category:Swimmers at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing Category:Male backstroke swimmers
